        <Parent_String>men's quarters [300260516], rooms and spaces by occupants [300075770], rooms and spaces [300133704], built work divisions [300072553], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
